fsrtool.name: fsrtool_eveorder_user_types
fsrtool.structure: CREATE TABLE `fsrtool_eveorder_user_types` ( `id` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `typeID` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `amount` double DEFAULT NULL, `timestamp` varchar(14) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `lastchange` varchar(14) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `status` smallint(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `supplier` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `comment` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `corpid` varchar(32) NOT NULL, `target` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
